Subject: [PATCH] ASoC: SOF: topology: Make scheduler widget parsing IPC agnostic
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 2141b55d9174c7aa5b32da95a2caa807a018968a
